{"tid":1007540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[MAGA] 美軍再派3750名士兵 墨西哥邊境執勤","createTime":"2019-02-03T23:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T01:37:50.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55249efbd5de5d31c9c6534afd187fd278765198","tid":1007540,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T23:46:09.000Z","msg":"美軍再派3750名士兵 墨西哥邊境執勤<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/2053602/%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%B4%BE3750%E5%90%8D%E5%A3%AB%E5%85%B5+%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83%E5%9F%B7%E5%8B%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2053602%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%25B4%25BE3750%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%2585%25B5%2B%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%2593%25A5%25E9%2582%258A%25E5%25A2%2583%25E5%259F%25B7%25E5%258B%25A4&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=c8a67f84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/2053602/%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%B4%BE3750%E5%90%8D%E5%A3%AB%E5%85%B5+%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83%E5%9F%B7%E5%8B%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國防部披露，五角大廈正派遣3750名士兵，至接壤墨西哥的邊境執行任務3個月，為邊境人員提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n連同現有在邊境執行支援任務的軍人，美國將有4350名士兵派駐在美墨邊境。五角大廈是在去年10月開始派遣軍隊到美墨邊境執行任務。<br />\n<br />\n根據周日的聲明，臨時國防部長沙納漢(Patrick Shanahan)是在1月11日批准本次派遣士兵的安排。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨籍的眾議院軍械服務委員會主席Adam Smith在上周四首次披露有關增加派軍的消息。他當時不滿五角大廈官員在聽證會上沒有披露有關消息。"},{"pid":"be25d71202da1e6edee973ee7e4c6e1602e04fe4","tid":1007540,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T00:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002dfa25b896d0237b30f1e776cc2a65d438e206","tid":1007540,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T01:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}